Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(956,52)}SELF-STUDY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you seriously going to help her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And what if I am? This isn't fair.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.06,0:00:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She didn't even do anything to them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, that's how bullying works.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only reason they need is not liking you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was looking at us.\NShe wanted us to help her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well duh, we were the only ones there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you're really sticking your nose into this, count me out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All you're going to get is them switching targets to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then what's going to happen to her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not my problem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.34,0:00:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Either she gets out of it somehow, or she just stops coming to school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or a teacher notices and steps in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.97,0:00:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So we should just abandon her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seriously, why are you like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.05,0:01:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just listening to you is getting annoying. I've had enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You’re not the only one!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get where you're coming from.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I can't accept this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're basically saying that the ones in the wrong are right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.65,0:01:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stand for it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have to go to the agency today?...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap, I overslept.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\2c&H0FFFFFF&\3c&HAAAAAA&\4c&HFFFFFF\i1\b1\fnSegoe Script\fs80\pos(1257.4,956.4)}ROCK'N'ROLL WON'T STOP RINGING
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be frank. We haven't managed to sell even half the expected amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No surprise there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,With that amount of views on the song,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no way we'd suddenly be that popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura-san, what's your take on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The biggest problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you’ve never had this much exposure before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If we look at search statistics, you're doing quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, this would significantly contribute to your view count.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're saying it didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the agency's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It means we haven't promoted the song well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no, that's not what I was going to say-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In the era of self-promotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,talent agencies need to evolve and adapt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's no benefit for the artist, there's no reason for them to belong to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a bit more time. I’ll come up with countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve never seen her like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a bit off, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, where’s Momoka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She just went “Sorry, see ya” and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She went back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't we going to rehearse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, let's just skip today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san noticed, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- Noticed what?\N - You're really dense, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what she said?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Our name gained traction, but our song didn't.  Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura knew that Momoka-san wanted to say exactly that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So she didn't let her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So Momoka-san doesn't get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not it! We just need to be patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an amazing song! Everyone was praising it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Miura-san and Nakata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If that was enough to sell your music, it wouldn't be a struggle in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's like Van Gogh only selling one painting in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,People follow trends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If everyone says something's great, you'll watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it's something no one cares about, you probably won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s not…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of two Let's Plays of the same game,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,would you click on the one with 5,000 views or the one with 1 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}THE NEXT DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Picking a fight they can't win."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}“I hate how pretentious they feel."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}“They should just quit like the losers they are.”{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw off, you didn't even listen to the song!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, we're not losing to {\i1}you{\i0}! Piss off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, calm down, calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The two-day battle's coming up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And Diamond Dust sold all their tickets...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No surprise there I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A follow request?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,From Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It has the verified mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Made you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you need a disguise or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not {\i1}that{\i0} famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You still like those, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. We used to eat those after school, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's my treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- So, what do you want?\N- Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought you might be misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Misunderstanding what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t become their new singer on purpose or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you about the auditions, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wait, that was after we stopped talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And you stopped coming to school by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So what, you came here just to gloat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell me that this is all because I didn't just do what you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That everything would be fine if I just listened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...is what I want to say, but that's only half-right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- Your tickets aren't selling, are they?\N- It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it is my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re playing together, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not "together"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your agent, Miura-san, paid us a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To ask us for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanted us to play on both days, since if we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,we can have a two-day duel with both days sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your concert's only filling the venue to 30% of its capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We can fit it in our schedule, so all that's left is for us to approve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought I might as well  ask what you think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying you don't need my help then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will you gratefully accept?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s called success. A very important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A crucial thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you just accept reality already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"I was wrong. And Hina was right all along."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Admit that you should've listened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll live by baring it all", was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Admit you were wrong, and I'll gladly come to your rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for calling you so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, like I've already told the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,DiaDust asked us if we want to play on both days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So that we can face off in front of the same audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Miura-san tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, what about it?\N- Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't even a fair fight before, so why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we go with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it would mean that most of our audience will be there for DiaDust.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that basically the same as admitting our defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're against this idea, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I get where you're coming from, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that. Never in a million years!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What did we get this far for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To prove that Momoka-san wasn't wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that her songs can reach people!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's always been our driving force!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But reality's not that kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We sold less than 30% of our tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worse than when we were an indie band.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:09:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to take responsibility then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how much money is at stake here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Money?\N- And I'm not talking just about the venue costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Merchandise, advertising. None of that is free you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to do what we can to mitigate the losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have to bow to DiaDust like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's bowing down to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly, we're just accepting their proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That {\i1}is{\i0} bowing down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think they just offered this out of the blue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura-san bowed down to them and asked for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She begged them to play with us. To help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanted me to admit that I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she'll help us all we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that I wasn't wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't just go bowing down to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't reject who I was back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Money, responsibility, popularity…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just frustrated… frustrated, frustrated, frustrated!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- Nina?\N- Nina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did they do this to you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought I told you already.\N I won't be on your side in this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:11:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did you really hate me sticking up for her that much?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, talking to you always gives me this unpleasant feeling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like you always radiate spikes of so-called justice, hurting everyone around you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It always makes me feel like I'm the bad guy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- And that was the end of your friendship.\N- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is definitely a Nina-like story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the bullied girl after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange really,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but she started bullying me with the others in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then one day she talked to me in secret, and asked me to apologize to the other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"They'll forgive you", she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I wouldn't have to be their target anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She was trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She was terrified of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But you helped her. She owes you, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how you stopped coming to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"I wasn't wrong", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But you {\i1}were{\i0} wrong, no matter you put it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But she was! No matter how you think about it, that Hina girl ended up being right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's part of why I was drawn to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I like your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And Rupa, Momoka, and Subaru probably do too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait, no, stop!\N- Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like this kinda stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we have our answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, Miura-san and the others worked hard for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll have to take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I can't say I didn't see it coming from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, very Nina-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're refusing the offer?\N- Yes, our apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They're offering you a fair fight, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, at this point it would just look like they came to our rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe so, but regarding the audience…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Withdrawal request{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We decided this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that it looks like\Na selfish whim of ours,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and how it hurts the agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us the exact costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say when, but we promise to cover them eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, raise your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,From DiaDust's Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly appreciate you going so far for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We only went for it because of my selfishness in the first place, and you still helped us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I realize it's rude of me to refuse this offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for my selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I did suspect that it would go against your principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm also to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But let's be clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The money and the contract are our responsibility, not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your personality that made me want to work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Withdrawal request{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,At least let me be useful to you at the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- For another agency?\N- No, we're thinking of going solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our own decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,(Nakata) Spoken like true greenhorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}- Is he mad?\N- We didn't need to give him details...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come see me in 10 years\Nif you survive until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you something for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We will! Thank you so much, Nakata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for some gyudon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You just want to get wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not fooling anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, this is where we met you two, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Beni-Shoga, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we make a promise? With you two as Beni-Shoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The name's special to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll add a special promise on top of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly are we promising?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To always stay together and never give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll have to eat together then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one drink, you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I love this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This city, where I met friends who would laugh and cry with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawasaki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We got wrecked, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like losing every match in the qualifying rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No miracles for us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well duh. We're not a soap opera.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, didn't know you like those.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I only watch \N{\i1}Detective Grandma's Case Files{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, it's not like we haven't seen it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We understood that reality's harsh, that it won't be easy for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who {\i1}didn't{\i0} understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't argue there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, guess you wouldn't be able to shout "I wasn't wrong" all the time otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, we got a lot more comments after yesterday's DiaDust concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you the one who told me {\i1}not{\i0} to look at those?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"I like them."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why are people hating on them?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh shut it, music isn’t about numbers."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's not over yet, don't just assume they lost."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,See, there are people who'd say these kinds of things for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we really reached them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I didn't know you got so good at playing the guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't see that coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure I should play on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you did spend a lot of time practicing in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:17:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(1532.8,656)}To Nina ♥ \N Look up!!{\i0} \N - Hina
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(961.6,518.4)}Look left ♥♥ \N - Hina{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Left?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,TOGENASHI TOGEARI
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(594.2,664)}{\i1\fnArial\fs100}Made you look ♥{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- That little...\N- She’s funny, I'll give her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that Hina doesn't actually want you to give up, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She went out of her way just to get you to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably because she knew you'd be stubborn and refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like the last boss of a video game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultra-annoying Demon Lord of Self-Righteousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If she beats you it's game over, but she wants to play with you some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee thanks, I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I’m right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright everyone, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm...you already know this,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but this was supposed to be a duel against Diamond Dust.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I guess the result is obvious...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, thank you all for coming today!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, we were really focused on it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beating Diamond Dust, I mean.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We didn't want to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were serious about it at the festival too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know it's sudden, but I'll be rambling about myself for a bit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rupa-san, can I?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I was in high school, I tried to help a girl who was being bullied.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On my way to where she was, I felt happy with my decision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I felt like someone I could really like and be proud of. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But then I became the new target,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I ended up dropping out of school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But still, I never thought that I made a mistake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never thought that maybe it'd be better if I didn't help her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now, I can say that I regret absolutely nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Momoka-san's song gave me the strength I needed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I always told Hina that-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hina loved their music too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It wasn’t just my song. It reached her too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once again, thank you all for coming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are the rebels who go against the grain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I love you all for that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will scream. Scream that we won’t give up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That we weren't wrong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(966.4,64)}{\i1}Please become the witnesses of our beginning!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're all the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H5D2529&\3c&HD38092&\fn@UD Digi Kyokasho NP-B}Dare datte onnaji{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Living on top of life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H5D2529&\3c&HD38092&\fn@UD Digi Kyokasho NP-B}Inochi no ue ni ikiteru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you can't find a place of your own{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H5D2529&\3c&HD38092&\fn@UD Digi Kyokasho NP-B}Ibasho ga nai nara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:21:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fly high{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:21:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H5D2529&\3c&HD38092&\fn@UD Digi Kyokasho NP-B}Tobidatte yuke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fate tangled up, reverberating{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had taken all the other paths{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H5D2529&\3c&HD38092&\fn@UD Digi Kyokasho NP-B}Unmei ga karamatte, todoroite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H5D2529&\3c&HD38092&\fn@UD Digi Kyokasho NP-B}Hokano michi yaritsukushite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I dedicate the rest of my life to singing with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H5D2529&\3c&HD38092&\fn@UD Digi Kyokasho NP-B}Watashi ni nokotta jinsei kimi to utatte iku koto{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No light or wind, like an isolated prison{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H5D2529&\3c&HD38092&\fn@UD Digi Kyokasho NP-B\fs56}Akari mo kaze mo nai, maru de koritsu na rougoku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pain and suffering\N Scars all over, I hated it all{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H5D2529&\3c&HD38092&\fn@UD Digi Kyokasho NP-B\fs52}Kurushikute tsurakute kizudarake de zenbu ga iya dattan da{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even with my wings full of holes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H5D2529&\3c&HD38092&\fn@UD Digi Kyokasho NP-B}Hirogeta tsubasa wa ana darake demo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even in the depths of hell, if I could sing with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H5D2529&\3c&HD38092&\fn@UD Digi Kyokasho NP-B}Jigoku no soko datte kimi to utaeru nara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I flew away, wanting to disappear{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H5D2529&\3c&HD38092&\fn@UD Digi Kyokasho NP-B}Kietakute, habataite ima{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But now I want to stay{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H5D2529&\3c&HD38092&\fn@UD Digi Kyokasho NP-B}Kietakunakunatta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I picked a budding bloom, waiting for it to blossom{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H5D2529&\3c&HD38092&\fn@UD Digi Kyokasho NP-B\fs60}Tsumitotte nokoshita koko de itsuka hana sakaseru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The me who wanted to disappear is gone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H5D2529&\3c&HD38092&\fn@UD Digi Kyokasho NP-B}Kietakatta watashi wa mou inai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm glad I didn't disappear{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H5D2529&\3c&HD38092&\fn@UD Digi Kyokasho NP-B}Kienakute yokatta na{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I met you\N And our flower of fate bloomed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H5D2529&\3c&HD38092&\fn@UD Digi Kyokasho NP-B\fs58}Datte kimi to deai, mebuite shimatta, unmei no hana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Three, two, one…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.38,0:22:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you!{\i0}
